Usage: check_power_intent [-help] -1801 -hierarchical [-outfile <string>]
                          [-verbose]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-1801                  # power intent is ieee1801 (bool, required)
-hierarchical          # input power intent style (bool, required)
-outfile <string>      # output filename (string, optional)
-verbose               # print more info (bool, optional)